game.name: A Day in Angel World
game.description:
Hey ladies! These two most beautiful and smart angels enjoy their life a lot in the sky. Their unmatched lifestyle is a center of attraction for many girls. Both of them happily spend their time with each other while enjoying their everyday life. You are also one of their biggest fans, and, luckily, you have gotten a wonderful opportunity to watch their living in a day. Are you ready, friends? Join A Day in Angel World and be prepared to witness the life of angel in the sky!

When you click the play button, you would see the two gorgeous princesses on the screen. Choose anyone out of the two and get ready to play with the multiple beauty items shown on the bottom of the screen! Start with the eye shadow and then make her face glow with the mask in this HTML5 make-up game! Give her cute lips a glossy lipstick and then change her eyes look with the matching eye lenses! Once make-up is done, move on the dressing part. 

Dress her up with a cream gown with a brown ribbon on the waist or choose a plan pink gown or light blue outfit with a purple ribbon gripped above the waist! You would also some out amazing outfit options to try out in this one of the best dressing games for girls. In the next step, give your girl a nice matching hairstyle and then a suitable tiara, wings, and a magical weapon. Follow the instructions for the second girl as well while getting her ready!
